  "introText": "你的笔记本里有了两个声音碎片。但现在出现了一个问题：一些生物躲了起来，只露出影子。你能仅凭声音认出它们吗？把右边的隐形生物拖到对应的匹配区——注意听它们的声音！",
  "introTextEn": "Your notebook has two sound fragments. But now: some creatures hide, showing only shadows. Can you identify them by sound? Drag the shadow creatures to their match zones — listen carefully!",
  "victoryText": "你仅凭声音就认出了它们！这证明声音有独一无二的特征——就像人的面孔一样。辨别声音是语言工程师的一项基本功。",
  "victoryTextEn": "You identified them by sound alone! Sounds have unique characteristics. Discriminating sounds is a fundamental skill of the Language Engineer.",
